        "question_eWU8W3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What skincare products should I use daily?",
            "answer": "<p>A simple routine includes a <a href=\"/collections/cleansers\" title=\"Vegan Face Wash and Facial Cleansers\">face wash</a>, <a href=\"/collections/serums\" title=\"Vegan Face Serums\">serum</a>, and <a href=\"/collections/moisturizers\" title=\"Vegan Moisturizers & Face Lotion\">moisturizer</a>. You can build a complete routine with skincare from Pacifica Beauty, including targeted treatments like the <a href=\"/products/glow-baby-booster-serum\" title=\"Glow Baby Booster Serum\">Glow Baby Booster Serum</a> for brightening support.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_cWQQNT": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are Pacifica Beauty skincare products vegan and cruelty-free?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, all skincare from Pacifica Beauty is 100% vegan and cruelty-free, with formulas designed to be gentle and suitable for a wide range of skin types and concerns.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_PTLygC": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What skin concerns do Pacifica skincare products target?",
            "answer": "<p>Pacifica skincare is designed to address concerns like dryness, dullness, acne, uneven texture and breakouts. Explore <a href=\"/collections/glow-baby\" title=\"Vitamin C Skincare for Bright, Glowing Skin\">brightening skincare</a>, <a href=\"/collections/acne\" title=\"Acne Skincare\">acne treatments</a>, and <a href=\"/collections/barrier-care\" title=\"Skin Barrier Repair & Sensitive Skincare\">barrier care skincare</a> to support your skin’s needs, including exfoliating treatments like the <a href=\"/products/glow-baby-brightening-peel-pads-10-aha-bha\" title=\"Glow Baby Brightening Peel Pads 10% AHA + BHA\">Glow Baby Brightening Peel Pads</a> from Pacifica Beauty, formulated with 10% AHA + BHA to exfoliate, retexturize, and reveal brighter, more glowing skin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_r4dhGN": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I choose the right skincare products for my skin type?",
            "answer": "<p>Choosing the right routine depends on your skin type and goals. Whether you need <a href=\"/collections/cleansers\" title=\"Vegan Face Wash and Facial Cleansers\">gentle cleansers</a>, <a href=\"/collections/moisturizers\" title=\"Vegan Moisturizers & Face Lotion\">hydrating face creams</a>, or <a href=\"/collections/serums\" title=\"Vegan Face Serums\">targeted serums</a>, Pacifica Beauty offers options for every skin type and concern.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_3xRQH3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why is cleansing important in a skincare routine?",
            "answer": "<p>Cleansing helps remove dirt, oil, and buildup while preparing your skin for treatments. Using a <a href=\"/collections/cleansers\" title=\"Vegan Face Wash and Facial Cleansers\">vegan face wash</a> regularly can help keep your skin feeling fresh, balanced, and ready for the next steps in your routine.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_JfhjMa": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What are the benefits of using a serum?",
            "answer": "<p>Serums deliver targeted results for concerns like hydration, brightness, texture, and visible signs of aging. Discover <a href=\"/collections/serums\" title=\"Vegan Face Serums\">face serums</a> from Pacifica Beauty, including advanced treatments like the <a href=\"/products/glow-baby-booster-serum\" title=\"Glow Baby Booster Serum\">Glow Baby Booster Serum</a> for visibly brighter, more even-looking skin, or the <a href=\"/products/wake-up-beautiful-retinoid-serum\" title=\"Wake Up Beautiful Retinoid Serum\">Wake Up Beautiful Retinoid Serum</a> to help smooth the look of fine lines and support a more refreshed complexion overnight.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_gYFzLT": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is barrier care in skincare?",
            "answer": "<p>Barrier care in skincare focuses on strengthening and protecting the skin barrier to help maintain hydration, reduce sensitivity, and support overall skin health and balance. Explore <a href=\"/collections/barrier-care\" title=\"Skin Barrier Repair & Sensitive Skincare\">barrier care skincare</a> from Pacifica Beauty, including targeted solutions like the <a href=\"/products/barrier-defense-hypochlorous-acid-daily-spray\" title=\"Barrier Defense Hypochlorous Acid Daily Spray\">Barrier Defense Hypochlorous Acid Daily Spray</a>, recognized by the National Psoriasis Foundation, designed to help soothe and support compromised or sensitive skin while reinforcing the skin’s natural barrier.</p>"
          }
        }
